==Introduction==

[[Help:Data Model|Data Model]] section describes how the underlying database data model is defined.
Based on that model basic user interface to add, view, modify and search data are generated.
To improve user experience the default, basic user interface can be further enriched by introduction of various '''Widgets'''.


There are two categories of Widgets:
* '''Implicit Widgets'''
:These widgets are added to the page automatically. They often depend on the Concept definition (e.g. existence of specific Properties, type of Concept, etc.). This category includes:
:* [[Help:Navigator|Navigator]]
:* [[Help:Related Data|Related Data]]
:* [[Help:Map|Map]]

* '''Explicit Widgets'''
:These widgets has to be specified in the model explicitly. This category includes:
:* [[Help:Group|Group]]
:* [[Help:Query|Query]]
::* [[Help:Property List|Property List]]
::* [[Help:Property Groups|Property Groups]]
::* [[Help:Reference|Reference]]
::* [[Help:ReferenceGroup|Reference Groups]]
:* [[Help:User Query|User Query]]
:* [[Help:Chart|Chart]]
:* [[Help:Gantt Chart|Gantt Chart]]
:* [[Help:Reports|Reports]]
:* [[Help:Static Content|Static Content]]
:* [[Help:Workflow|Workflow]]
:* [[Help:Conditional|Conditional]]
:* [[Help:Help Information|Help Information]]


==Definition==
The explicit widgets are being defined among Concept properties within the "structure" element.

The location of the widgets determines its location on the rendered page.

<pre>
  <concept name="{NAME}">
    <structure>
      <{WIDGET1} {PARAMETERS}>
        <property name="Property A"/>
        <property name="Property B"/>
        <property name="Property C"/>
        <{WIDGET2} {PARAMETERS}/>
        <property name="Property D"/>
      </{WIDGET1}>
      <property name="Property 1"/>
      <property name="Property 2"/>
      <{WIDGET3} {PARAMETERS}/>
    </structure>
  </concept>
</pre>


==Semantic Database==
The widgets don't modify a content of semantic database, but instead provide custom data visualizations.


==Example==
<pre>
  <concept name="Event">
    <structure>
      <property name="Title"/>
      <property name="Start date"/>
      <property name="End date"/>
      <property name="Is executed on" refersTo="Enclave"/>                  <!-- triggers Related Data Widget -->
    </structure>
  </concept>

  <concept name="Enclave">                                                   <!-- Navigator Widget is always visible -->
    <structure>
      <property name="Title" mandatory="true"/>
      <property name="Description" mandatory="true"/>
      <property name="Classification"/>
      <group name="Period">                                                  <!-- Group Widget -->
        <property name="Start date"/>
        <property name="End date"/>
      </group>
      <reference name="Sites"  refersFrom="Site" property="Is part of"/>     <!-- Reference Widget -->
    </structure>
    <reports>                                                                <!-- Reports Widget -->
      <report name="Enclave Infrastructure" scope="instance"/>
    </reports>
  </concept>

  <concept name="Site">
    <structure>
      <property name="Title" mandatory="true"/>
      <property name="Description" mandatory="true"/>
      <property name="Is part of" refersTo="Enclave">
        <relatedData format="table">
          <columns>
            <column name="Title"/>
            <column name="Description"/>
          </columns>
        </relatedData>
      </property>
      <property name="Coordinates"/>                                         <!-- triggers Map Widgets -->
    </structure>
  </concept>

</pre>


